title: Power of 292 quadrillion 103 trillion 482 billion 193 million 583 thousand and 293

fields.name: Abilities:
fields.value: - Select a player, and choose a Town alignment. You will use the abilities of 292 quadrillion 103 trillion 482 billion 193 million 583 thousand and 293 random roles from that alignment on your target.

fields.name: Attributes:
fields.value:
- You can target yourself.
- Roles can repeat.
